    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Firmamus atque
                        constituemus nos domna gloriosissima <persName ref="#people/2002"
                            >Scauniperga</persName> et domnus <rs key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis"
                            >vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/374" key="#Marquis/duke">Liutprand</persName> summi
                            <rs key="#Marquis/duke">ducibus</rs> gentis Langubardorum, <rs
                            key="#Intercessory">per rogum</rs>
                        <persName key="#Intercessory #Marepahis" ref="#people/3648"
                            >Radoald</persName>
                        <rs key="#Marepahis">marepahis</rs> nostro, libertatem tibi mulieri nomine
                            <name ref="Cunda">Cunda</name> cum filia tua <name ref="Liuperga"
                            >Liuperga</name> quem de <name ref="Ansebrandus">Ansprando</name>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clericus</rs> procreatam habusti vel in antea
                        procreaberit, iuxta ut nos ipse Ansprando postulavit et in nostris tradedit
                        manibus ut nos iuxta ritus gentis Langobardorum libera fufreal constituere,
                        quod et eiusdem audientem postulationem in nostrorum fidelium ipse
                        Ansprandus in nostris tradedit manu, nos eam tradedimus in manu <persName
                            ref="#people/3649" key="#Other_palatine_officer">Theautpald</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer">duddi et referendarii</rs>, et Theautpald
                        te tradedit in manu Iohanni <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer"
                            >stolesatiu</rs>, <persName ref="#people/3647"
                            key="#Other_palatine_officer">Iohannis</persName> tradedit in manu
                            <persName ref="#people/3650" key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus"
                            >Radoaldi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">gastaldi</rs> nostro, hoc est in quarta
                        manu te tradedimus, qui te per nostram iussionem witrepora in gahida et
                        gisel fulfreale constituit una cum filia tua in omnem tua substantia
                        hereditabi, quatenus amodo et deinceps <rs key="#Arimannus #Manumission"
                            >libera inter libertes aremanne dominorum nostrorum</rs> here
                        inbeniaris, et nullus ex nostris gastaldeis aut actionarii vel quisquam homo
                        contra ea que nostra firmabit potestas quandoque ire presumat, sed nostra
                        firmitas roborata permaneat Quod vero preceptum libertatem firmitatis ex
                        iussione nominate potestati dictabi ego <persName ref="#people/3649"
                            key="#Other_palatine_officer">Theautpald</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer">duddus et referendarius</rs> tibi
                            <persName ref="#people/3651" key="#Notary">Radichis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notario</rs> scribendum. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/3468"
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Fiscal_property #Residential #Palatium">ad
                            Rosito</placeName> mense decembrio, indictione sexta. Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
